snippet.title: Smintheus - Beta - Trailer
snippet.description:
Smintheus (Beta) is a 2D puzzle adventure game with crafting and survival RPG elements. Complete solo indie game project by Henrik Chukhran.

Game link: https://neutonmouse.itch.io/smintheus
Website: http://www.neutonmouse.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/neutonmouse
